qDef.qDef:
pick(match(KPI_ID, 10, 20, 30, 40, 50, 51, 52, 60, 70, 80, 90, 100, 110), 
//'EXP1',
'',//num([Doses distributed], '#,##0'),
//'EXP2',
num(100*min({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>} aggr(nodistinct SUM({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}, DosesDistributed_per100Inh={">0"}>} DosesDistributed_per100Inh_Cumul), [Member State])), '#,##0.0') & ' - '& 
num(100*max({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>} aggr(nodistinct SUM({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}, DosesDistributed_per100Inh={">0"}>} DosesDistributed_per100Inh_Cumul), [Member State])), '#,##0.0'),
// Expr 30
'',//num(sum(DoseTotal_ALLP), '#,##0'),
//'EXP4',
num(100* min({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}Uptake1st_ALL_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0')  & ' - ' &  
num(max({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}Uptake1st_ALL_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0%'),
//'EXP5',
num(100* min({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}Uptake2nd_ALL_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0')  & ' - ' &  
num(max({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}Uptake2nd_ALL_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0%'),

num(100* min({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}Uptake1st_ALLP_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0')  & ' - ' &  
num(max({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}Uptake1st_ALLP_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0%'),
//'EXP5',
num(100* min({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}Uptake2nd_ALLP_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0')  & ' - ' &  
num(max({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}Uptake2nd_ALLP_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0%'),

num(100*min(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_80_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_80_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0') & ' - ' &
num(rangemin(1, max(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_80_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_80_Cumul), [Member State]))), '0%'),

num(100*min(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake2nd_80_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake2nd_80_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0') & ' - ' &
num(rangemin(1, max(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake2nd_80_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake2nd_80_Cumul), [Member State]))), '0%'),

num(100*min(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_HCW_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_HCW_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0') & ' - ' &
num(rangemin(1, max(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_HCW_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_HCW_Cumul), [Member State]))), '0%'),

num(100*min(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"},  Uptake2nd_HCW_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake2nd_HCW_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0') & ' - ' &
num(rangemin(1, max(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"},  Uptake2nd_HCW_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake2nd_HCW_Cumul), [Member State]))), '0%'),

num(100*min(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_LTCF_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_LTCF_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0') & ' - ' &
num(rangemin(1, max(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_LTCF_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_LTCF_Cumul), [Member State]))), '0%'),

num(100*min(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"},  Uptake2nd_LTCF_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake2nd_LTCF_Cumul), [Member State])), '0.0') & ' - ' &
num(rangemin(1, max(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"},  Uptake2nd_LTCF_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake2nd_LTCF_Cumul), [Member State]))), '0%')
)

='Key figures of the COVID-19 vaccine rollout in ' & v_EU27_EEA_Title
